descriptionHtml:
Description
	Simple quest expanding civil war.
	Ever thought why Tullius/Ulfric left field operations to an enemy?
	I was. Fixing.
	Go talk to General Tullius/Ulfric Stormcloak
	after completing Imperial/Stormcloaks questline.
	Ask, what you can do for the cause.
	No overpowering items, overwealthing rewards.

Installing
	Nexus Mod Manager will do
	OR
	Move files from archive to Data folder,
	check in skyrim launcher data files.

Compatibility
	May be incompatible with mods that alters
	ActorBase for field commanders and CWFin quest.

History
	v0.1 beta
		Beta means need testing.
		Report here on Nexus in discussion.

Permissions
	Do what you want with it.
author: bsjadhcbas
